:: scene_01_opening
The evening is settling. What do you do next?
[[Go inside for dinner->scene_02_track2]]
[[Finish weaving the hammock->scene_02_track1]]

:: scene_02_track1
You stay with the weave; voices drift from the house. How do you respond?
[[Peek out the window->scene_03_t1_peek]]
[[Join the huddle->scene_03_t1_huddle]]

:: scene_02_track2
You head in for dinner, but something outside still pulls at you.
[[Watch them pass by->scene_03_t2_watch]]
[[Go inside->scene_03_t2_inside]]

:: scene_03_t1_peek
The glass frames a small, decisive moment. The story leans toward the peek ending.

:: scene_03_t1_huddle
You step toward the circle of voices. The story leans toward the huddle ending.

:: scene_03_t2_watch
You stay to watch — long enough that the right move is to step back and begin again.

:: scene_03_t2_inside
Inside, the house exhales. You can still change what you witness next.
[[Peek outside->ending_peek]]
[[Join the huddle->ending_huddle]]

:: ending_peek
The peek ending — a held breath, then release.

:: ending_huddle
The huddle ending — warmth and weight together.

:: return_title_watch
The loop back from watching — a breath before the opening returns.

:: return_title_from_end
Return from the endings — one minute in the story, then back to the start.
